\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {2}{\ignorespaces The discovery cascade on a real batch (2026-06-07, AI-supply-chain). Bar \emph  {length} is the candidate count surviving each stage; bar \emph  {fill} is the model cost tier (white $=$ deterministic, no LLM). The dedup step removes duplicates, not ideas; the expensive model judges only the survivors and admitted \textbf  {none} this session --- this is rejection, not throughput, and ``no action'' is the modal outcome.}}{16}{figure.2}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:cascade}{{2}{16}{The discovery cascade on a real batch (2026-06-07, AI-supply-chain). Bar \emph {length} is the candidate count surviving each stage; bar \emph {fill} is the model cost tier (white $=$ deterministic, no LLM). The dedup step removes duplicates, not ideas; the expensive model judges only the survivors and admitted \textbf {none} this session --- this is rejection, not throughput, and ``no action'' is the modal outcome}{figure.2}{}}
